# Action Item Format

All action items use checkbox format for consistency.

## Syntax

```markdown
- [ ] Task description @Owner 📅 YYYY-MM-DD ⏫ ([source](path/to/note.md))
```

## Elements

| Element | Format | Required |
|---|---|---|
| Checkbox | `- [ ]` open, `- [x]` done | Yes |
| Description | Free text describing the task | Yes |
| Owner | `@Name` | Yes |
| Due date | `📅 YYYY-MM-DD` | Only if deadline known |
| Priority | `⏫` high, `🔼` medium, `🔽` low | Optional |
| Source | `([display](path/to/note.md))` | Yes |

## Canonical Location

Open tasks live in `**/Summary.md` files, not in individual meeting notes.
When summarizing meetings, merge action items into Summary.md:
1. New items: add as `- [ ]`
2. Completed items: change to `- [x]`
3. Duplicates: merge into one entry using earliest source
